---
// HeroSection.astro
---

<section
  class="relative w-full h-screen min-h-[600px] sm:h-[100vh] overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
>
  <!-- Video de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <video
      src="/Video/video.mp4"
      autoplay
      loop
      muted
      playsinline
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"></video>
    <!-- Overlay sutil para mejorar legibilidad del texto -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-pink-500/10"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTENIDO CENTRAL -->
  <main
    class="relative z-10 flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 sm:px-6"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight drop-shadow-2xl"
    >
      Desarrollo de páginas web que<br />
      convierten y venden
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 max-w-2xl text-white/90 text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium px-2"
    >
      Diseño y desarrollo landing pages, sitios corporativos y tiendas en línea
      que transforman visitantes en clientes reales. Moderno, rápido y enfocado
      en resultados.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-center justify-center">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/522288535112?text=Hola,%20quiero%20una%20cotización"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="px-8 py-3 sm:px-10 sm:py-4 bg-white text-gray-900 font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-widest rounded-full
               shadow-2xl hover:bg-pink-50 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95
               transition-all duration-300 ease-out cursor-pointer inline-block"
      >
        Cotizar gratis
      </a>
      <a
        href="/proyectos"
        class="px-8 py-3 sm:px-10 sm:py-4 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-widest rounded-full
               shadow-2xl hover:bg-white/30 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95
               transition-all duration-300 ease-out cursor-pointer inline-block border border-white/30"
      >
        Ver proyectos
      </a>
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="px-8 py-3 sm:px-10 sm:py-4 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-widest rounded-full
               shadow-2xl hover:bg-white/30 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95
               transition-all duration-300 ease-out cursor-pointer inline-block border border-white/30"
      >
        Ver blog
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</section>
